One suspect has been shot and killed following an attempted hijacking at the Glen shopping centre on Tuesday morning.According to police spokesperson Lungelo Dlamini, four men tried to rob a courier van at the centre when security guards opened fire at them.&#8220;It is still unclear what was inside the courier Van which made it the target of these four armed robbers,&#8221; said Dlamini.Dlaminin also stated that the police are still searching for the three suspects who fled from the scene. They attempted to rob a courier van which was going to deliver goods. The suspects fled the scene. Police are searching for them, Dlamini said.-TNA Reporter